Subject: ALSA: hda - Add mic quirk for the Lenovo G50-30 (17aa:3905)

From: Jeremy Cline <jcline@redhat.com>

commit e7bb6ad5685f05685dd8a6a5eda7bfcd14d5f95b upstream.

